Denso bid - only on share repurchase report . Denso Corp shares were bid - only in Tuesday morning trade on media reports that the firm was planning a share repurchase , brokers said . Denso officials declined to comment on the report . As of 0123 GMT , the shares of the Toyota group firm were bid - only at 3 , 050 yen , after closing at 2 , 880 yen on Friday . Japanese markets were closed on Monday for a national holiday . 
